THE STORY
---------

You are an alien who was captured by the U.S. Government at Roswell. Your goal
is to escape the laboratory and find your flying saucer so that you can get
back home...

INSTALLATION
------------

Before trying to run this game, please adjust the +data-directory+ variable in
roswell.lisp to point to the appropriate directory where you installed Roswell
(or at least where you installed its data files). Be sure to include the
trailing slash, as file and subdirectory names are simply appended to it...
